text: Eugène Richez was an archer from France. He was born on 5 August 1864 and died on 31 October 1944. Richez competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and at the 1920 Summer Olympics.Eugène RichezEugène RICHEZ == References == Category:1864 births Category:1944 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for France Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France
